code: public void setId(int id) {     this.id = id. }
public void setName(String name) {     this.name = name. }

@Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o) {         return true.     }     if (!(o instanceof Pojo)) {         return false.     }     Pojo pojo = (Pojo) o.     if (id != pojo.getId()) {         return false.     }     return name != null ? name.equals(pojo.getName()) : pojo.getName() == null. }
@Override public int hashCode() {     int result = id.     result = 31 * result + (name != null ? name.hashCode() : 0).     return result. }
@Override public String toString() {     return "Pojo{" + "id=" + id + ", name='" + name + '\'' + '}'. }
